        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The clause refers to ‘the house’. Some understand ‘God’ as the antecedent to ‘which’; but see note on a similar interpretation in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
